graph TB
    subgraph "RHODS Operator (3 replicas)"
        Manager[Operator Manager<br/>Deployment]
        DSCIController[DSCInitialization Controller]
        DSCController[DataScienceCluster Controller]
        CompControllers[Component Controllers<br/>15+ components]
        SvcControllers[Service Controllers<br/>Auth, Monitoring, Gateway]
        Webhook[Webhook Server<br/>9443/TCP HTTPS]
        Metrics[Metrics Service<br/>8080/TCP HTTP]
        HealthProbes[Health Probes<br/>8081/TCP HTTP]

        Manager -->|manages| DSCIController
        Manager -->|manages| DSCController
        Manager -->|manages| CompControllers
        Manager -->|manages| SvcControllers
        Manager -->|exposes| Webhook
        Manager -->|exposes| Metrics
        Manager -->|exposes| HealthProbes
    end

    subgraph "Custom Resources Watched"
        DSCI[DSCInitialization CR]
        DSC[DataScienceCluster CR]
        Components[Component CRs<br/>Dashboard, Workbenches, Kserve, etc.]
        Services[Service CRs<br/>Monitoring, Auth, Gateway]
    end

    subgraph "Resources Created"
        Dashboard[ODH Dashboard]
        KServeOp[KServe Operator]
        Pipelines[Kubeflow Pipelines]
        ModelRegistry[Model Registry Operator]
        NotebookCtrl[Notebook Controller]
        RayOp[Ray Operator]
        TrainingOp[Training Operator]
        MonStack[Monitoring Stack<br/>Prometheus, Grafana]
        ServiceMesh[Service Mesh Config]
    end

    subgraph "External Dependencies"
        K8sAPI[Kubernetes API<br/>6443/TCP HTTPS]
        CertManager[Cert Manager /<br/>OpenShift Service CA]
        PrometheusOp[Prometheus Operator]
        Istio[Istio / Service Mesh]
        Knative[Knative Serving]
        OAuth[OpenShift OAuth]
    end

    User[User<br/>kubectl/oc] -->|creates| DSC
    User -->|creates| DSCI

    DSCI -->|watched by| DSCIController
    DSC -->|watched by| DSCController
    Components -->|watched by| CompControllers
    Services -->|watched by| SvcControllers

    DSCIController -->|configures| MonStack
    DSCIController -->|configures| ServiceMesh

    DSCController -->|deploys| Dashboard
    DSCController -->|deploys| KServeOp
    DSCController -->|deploys| Pipelines
    DSCController -->|deploys| ModelRegistry
    DSCController -->|deploys| NotebookCtrl
    DSCController -->|deploys| RayOp
    DSCController -->|deploys| TrainingOp

    CompControllers -->|reconciles| Components
    SvcControllers -->|reconciles| Services

    Manager -->|API calls| K8sAPI
    Webhook -->|validated by| K8sAPI
    Manager -->|uses certs from| CertManager
    DSCIController -->|creates| PrometheusOp
    DSCController -->|configures| Istio
    DSCController -->|configures| Knative
    Manager -->|authenticates via| OAuth

    Prometheus[Prometheus] -->|scrapes| Metrics

    style Manager fill:#4a90e2,stroke:#333,stroke-width:3px
    style DSCIController fill:#4a90e2,stroke:#333
    style DSCController fill:#4a90e2,stroke:#333
    style CompControllers fill:#4a90e2,stroke:#333
    style DSCI fill:#f5a623,stroke:#333
    style DSC fill:#f5a623,stroke:#333
    style Dashboard fill:#7ed321,stroke:#333
    style KServeOp fill:#7ed321,stroke:#333
    style Pipelines fill:#7ed321,stroke:#333
    style ModelRegistry fill:#7ed321,stroke:#333
    style K8sAPI fill:#999,stroke:#333
    style CertManager fill:#999,stroke:#333
    style Istio fill:#999,stroke:#333
